reviewText: Great product - I LOVE it!!!  What a smooth transaction!

Well worth the money. It has met my expectation and i would say it has all those detail that you want. Well packed with info and rare footage. I highly recommend to those who are interested to the Kennedy Family and the 34th President of the United States. Overall, This is a great item for collectors and you should buy this and you won't regret.
This set offers terrific insight into the Kennedy Family, their flaws, their triumphs and their history.

I bought the Kennedy megaset to gain more information about America's first family. I am very glad that I made the purchase because it contains many programs that are also for sale on amazon but it was all together in one set at a better price! I would recommend this set to others because the programs are very well done.
